Huawei is running its Huawei Watch Fit Bundle Sale, which includes great deals on products purchased in combination with the Huawei Watch Fit. These deals offer customers up to 30% off some of the coolest Huawei smartphones and gadgets. You can get the Huawei P40 Lite smartphone, as well as a smart scale and the Huawei Watch Fit, for just R8,799 – which means you save R1,599. If you’re in the market for a premium smartphone, you can buy the Huawei P40 Pro and get a smart scale and the Huawei Watch Fit for a combined price of just R22,799. The full selection of Huawei Watch Fit Bundle deals can be found on the Huawei store. Additionally, Huawei products are now on sale on the Jumia online storefront, providing another way to get your favourite Huawei gadgets at excellent prices. Some of the coolest deals from the Huawei Watch Fit Bundle Sale, as well great deals from the Jumia online storefront, can be found below. <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-370767" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-Y7P-deals-640x430.jpg" alt="Huawei Y7P deals" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-Y7P-deals-640x430.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-Y7P-deals-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-Y7P-deals-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-Y7P-deals-768x516.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-Y7P-deals-1536x1032.jpg 1536w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-Y7P-deals-1200x806.jpg 1200w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-Y7P-deals.jpg 1786w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-370769" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploa